properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 5 at 3:17AM EST until February 5 at 9:00PM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 38 kt and
waves 7 to 12 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Western Lake Superior.

* WHEN...From 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ this morning to 9 PM EST /8
PM CST/ this evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM EST /9 AM CST/ THIS MORNING TO 9 PM EST /8 PM CST/ THIS EVENING
